snippet.title: SHE OUT FISHED ME....TOMOKA RIVER BLACK DRUM FISHING
snippet.description:
Amber and I got a late start. We decided to try the Tomoka river for some great eating black drum. 
We were using dead shrimp on the bottom along bridge posts to catch these delicious fish.
